1
00:00:09,069 --> 00:00:09,865
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:18,838
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,041
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,717 --> 00:00:26,379
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,488 --> 00:00:30,116
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,825 --> 00:00:34,919
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,563 --> 00:00:38,691
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,167 --> 00:00:44,536
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,174 --> 00:00:48,937
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,043 --> 00:00:50,772
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,844 --> 00:00:53,176
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,715 --> 00:00:56,478
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,550 --> 00:00:58,450
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,519 --> 00:01:00,953
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,856 --> 00:01:09,420
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,531 --> 00:01:13,022
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,801 --> 00:01:16,668
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,508 --> 00:01:22,805
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,279 --> 00:01:26,803
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:34,499 --> 00:01:36,194
Hey, you there.

21
00:01:36,868 --> 00:01:37,596
Identify yourself.

22
00:01:38,302 --> 00:01:39,792
I'm not obliged to answer...

23
00:01:40,471 --> 00:01:41,369
What...?!

24
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:43,929
<i>Cute...</i>

25
00:01:49,047 --> 00:01:52,175
So those are Kakashi and
Guy's treasured brats...

26
00:01:52,817 --> 00:01:56,344
Well, for the time being,
their applications will pass.

27
00:01:56,754 --> 00:01:57,584
Yeah...

28
00:01:59,490 --> 00:02:02,118
It appears this year's
test takers will be amusing.

29
00:02:03,528 --> 00:02:05,462
For us proctors too, eh...

30
00:02:06,531 --> 00:02:09,193
Now then!
Sasuke, Naruto, let's go!

31
00:02:09,967 --> 00:02:10,865
Don't pull.

32
00:02:18,142 --> 00:02:21,270
<i>Sasuke... Sasuke Uchiha, eh.</i>

33
00:02:25,683 --> 00:02:28,083
Does that kid concern you?

34
00:02:28,686 --> 00:02:29,516
Hmph...

35
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,257
Lee, let's go.

36
00:02:37,361 --> 00:02:38,794
What're you doing?

37
00:02:39,163 --> 00:02:43,657
You guys go on ahead.
I have something I want to check out.

38
00:02:46,437 --> 00:02:47,495
What's that about?

39
00:02:47,739 --> 00:02:48,865
Why should I know?

40
00:02:55,146 --> 00:02:57,808
You, with the unpleasant look.
Wait a minute!

41
00:02:59,717 --> 00:03:00,308
Huh?

42
00:03:05,857 --> 00:03:06,915
- Oh!
- Yikes!

43
00:03:09,527 --> 00:03:10,255
What is it?

44
00:03:10,762 --> 00:03:13,356
Why don't you fight with me
here now?

45
00:03:13,664 --> 00:03:19,603
<i>Chunin Challenge.</i>
<i>Rock Lee vs. Sasuke!</i>

46
00:03:21,539 --> 00:03:23,404
A fight here now...?

47
00:03:24,242 --> 00:03:24,936
Yes.

48
00:03:31,749 --> 00:03:33,376
My name's Rock Lee.

49
00:03:34,852 --> 00:03:36,547
When asking a person their name,

50
00:03:36,621 --> 00:03:38,851
I'm supposed to give
my own name first, right?

51
00:03:39,557 --> 00:03:40,751
Sasuke Uchiha...

52
00:03:41,392 --> 00:03:43,690
Hmph... So you knew?

53
00:03:45,730 --> 00:03:46,890
I want to fight with you!

54
00:03:49,233 --> 00:03:52,100
I want to test out how effective
my techniques will be

55
00:03:52,837 --> 00:03:56,329
against the descendant of the
clan reputed for genius Ninjas.

56
00:03:57,408 --> 00:03:58,067
Also...

57
00:04:03,381 --> 00:04:05,747
Sakura. Love.

58
00:04:06,083 --> 00:04:10,986
Noooo!
Those lower eyelashes are awful!

59
00:04:11,823 --> 00:04:12,949
The hairstyle is awful, too!

60
00:04:13,090 --> 00:04:16,059
Those bushy eyebrows,
just too intense!

61
00:04:16,127 --> 00:04:17,287
Everything is!

62
00:04:17,662 --> 00:04:19,755
You're an angel!

63
00:04:21,766 --> 00:04:24,530
Noooooo!

64
00:04:27,038 --> 00:04:30,030
You are good at it.
Then, how about?

65
00:04:47,792 --> 00:04:49,089
<i>Really... That was super close.</i>

66
00:04:49,927 --> 00:04:52,487
You! Don't throw strange stuff!

67
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,957
I was dodging for my life!

68
00:04:56,667 --> 00:04:58,532
You don't have to resent me that much.

69
00:04:59,604 --> 00:05:02,903
<i>It's Sasuke again!</i>
<i>Darn it! Darn it!</i>

70
00:05:03,307 --> 00:05:06,174
To be honest, you're a naive one,

71
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:09,643
knowing the name of Uchiha
and challenging me.

72
00:05:10,781 --> 00:05:15,150
Do you want to realize
what this name is, Bushy Brow?

73
00:05:17,255 --> 00:05:18,017
I insist.

74
00:05:18,890 --> 00:05:19,948
<i>I'm lucky...</i>

75
00:05:20,191 --> 00:05:23,786
<i>to be able to have a bout with</i>
<i>the number one rookie right away.</i>

76
00:05:24,929 --> 00:05:27,762
<i>And, I'll prove it to you, Guy Sensei!</i>

77
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:29,696
Wait!

78
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:41,978
I AM going to take out
the Bushy Brow. Believe it!

79
00:05:43,314 --> 00:05:44,804
Hey, you!

80
00:05:44,882 --> 00:05:45,906
Big deal.

81
00:05:45,983 --> 00:05:47,951
I'll be able to take care of him
in just five minutes!

82
00:05:48,452 --> 00:05:52,320
The one I want to fight isn't you...
It's Uchiha.

83
00:05:53,591 --> 00:05:55,149
All these people...

84
00:05:55,593 --> 00:05:57,959
keep saying Sasuke, Sasuke.
How annoying!

85
00:06:12,043 --> 00:06:13,704
Darn it!

86
00:06:14,679 --> 00:06:15,941
Leaf Whirlwind!

87
00:06:23,354 --> 00:06:25,515
<i>As I thought, he's strong...</i>

88
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:31,986
I declare. You are absolutely
no match for me.

89
00:06:32,463 --> 00:06:33,452
Because...

90
00:06:34,932 --> 00:06:39,528
among the Leaf Village Genin,
I'm the strongest now.

91
00:06:46,477 --> 00:06:47,944
<i>He stopped my kick...</i>

92
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:50,611
<i>What's with that Chakra in his arm...?</i>

93
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:56,215
Interesting. I'll do it.

94
00:06:58,923 --> 00:06:59,514
Oh...

95
00:07:02,393 --> 00:07:03,690
Stop! Sasuke!

96
00:07:04,328 --> 00:07:07,695
There's less than thirty minutes
until the 3:00 registration.

97
00:07:08,899 --> 00:07:10,196
Don't worry.

98
00:07:11,969 --> 00:07:13,436
It'll be over in five minutes.

99
00:07:14,905 --> 00:07:15,496
<i>Here he comes!</i>

100
00:07:16,307 --> 00:07:18,002
<i>I'm sorry, Guy Sensei.</i>

101
00:07:18,609 --> 00:07:20,804
<i>I may end up breaking the taboo.</i>

102
00:07:20,878 --> 00:07:23,369
<i>I may end up using...</i>
<i>that technique!</i>

103
00:07:27,218 --> 00:07:28,617
Leaf Hurricanes!

104
00:07:31,822 --> 00:07:33,084
<i>I can't get completely out</i>
<i>of the way...</i>

105
00:07:33,157 --> 00:07:33,851
<i>Guard!</i>

106
00:07:35,926 --> 00:07:36,620
<i>What...?!</i>

107
00:07:37,862 --> 00:07:38,760
Sasuke!

108
00:07:47,838 --> 00:07:49,863
W-What's going on?

109
00:07:51,142 --> 00:07:54,578
<i>But...he did guard himself</i>
<i>just now, no mistake.</i>

110
00:07:56,347 --> 00:07:58,076
<i>He got around my guard.</i>

111
00:07:58,649 --> 00:07:59,445
<i>What is it?</i>

112
00:07:59,517 --> 00:08:02,213
<i>Is it Ninjutsu...?</i>
<i>Or is it Genjutsu...?!</i>

113
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:05,416
<i>As I thought, he's going to get up!</i>

114
00:08:06,323 --> 00:08:08,018
<i>Hmph... That's okay.</i>

115
00:08:08,926 --> 00:08:09,950
<i>If that's the case,</i>

116
00:08:10,027 --> 00:08:12,359
<i>this is a good opportunity</i>
<i>to get used to THAT.</i>

117
00:08:13,464 --> 00:08:15,455
I'll do it.

118
00:08:21,072 --> 00:08:24,166
<i>Huh?! C-Could that be...?</i>

119
00:08:25,876 --> 00:08:26,808
<i>Sharingan!</i>

120
00:08:27,511 --> 00:08:31,504
<i>Sasuke, when has he...</i>
<i>Why is that in his eyes...</i>

121
00:08:32,683 --> 00:08:33,809
<i>And in both eyes...!</i>

122
00:08:35,119 --> 00:08:36,746
<i>Is that the Sharingan?</i>

123
00:08:44,595 --> 00:08:46,893
<i>Sasuke's awesome, after all!</i>

124
00:08:48,265 --> 00:08:51,257
<i>If this is the same Kekkei Genkai</i>
<i>as Kakashi Sensei's...</i>

125
00:08:51,769 --> 00:08:53,703
<i>he can read Bushy Brow's Jutsu!</i>

126
00:08:54,505 --> 00:08:56,234
<i>Genjutsu or Ninjutsu...</i>

127
00:08:56,307 --> 00:09:01,301
<i>It's some kind of magic either way...</i>
<i>I'll reveal that!</i>

128
00:09:04,215 --> 00:09:06,911
<i>It feels like Sasuke's rapidly</i>
<i>getting stronger.</i>

129
00:09:10,454 --> 00:09:12,183
<i>That's to be expected</i>
<i>of the Uchiha clan.</i>

130
00:09:14,725 --> 00:09:18,661
<i>That's right...</i>
<i>Sasuke should not lose to a guy like this.</i>

131
00:09:23,567 --> 00:09:24,295
<i>Huh?!</i>

132
00:09:24,969 --> 00:09:25,936
<i>The Sharingan...!</i>

133
00:09:26,937 --> 00:09:29,337
<i>To not be able to discern the Jutsu</i>
<i>with the Sharingan...</i>

134
00:09:29,673 --> 00:09:32,073
<i>Could it be...that his technique is...!</i>

135
00:09:33,777 --> 00:09:34,436
That's right...

136
00:09:34,678 --> 00:09:37,408
My technique is neither
Ninjutsu nor Genjutsu.

137
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:45,012
S-Sasuke!

138
00:09:50,995 --> 00:09:51,859
That's right!

139
00:09:52,863 --> 00:09:57,163
My technique is
mere Taijutsu... Sasuke.

140
00:09:59,603 --> 00:10:02,094
You may not be able to
believe it just like that, but...

141
00:10:02,206 --> 00:10:03,138
Punk!

142
00:10:06,243 --> 00:10:08,939
It's said that the Sharingan has
the ability to spot

143
00:10:09,013 --> 00:10:13,143
all Genjutsu, Taijutsu and Ninjutsu.

144
00:10:14,552 --> 00:10:15,644
Make no mistake,

145
00:10:15,719 --> 00:10:18,483
the Sharingan reads Ninjutsu
and Genjutsu that

146
00:10:18,556 --> 00:10:20,547
require the principle of building up
Chakra and weaving Signs,

147
00:10:20,624 --> 00:10:22,717
and can most surely handle such Jutsu.

148
00:10:23,761 --> 00:10:27,162
However, only Taijutsu is
a little bit different...

149
00:10:27,531 --> 00:10:29,294
W-What do you mean?!

150
00:10:30,067 --> 00:10:32,661
Even if you can spot my movements
with the Sharingan,

151
00:10:33,170 --> 00:10:38,233
your body is not equipped with
the speed to respond to my Taijutsu.

152
00:10:39,577 --> 00:10:41,670
In other words, even if you understand
with your eyes,

153
00:10:41,745 --> 00:10:44,714
there's nothing you can do if your
body can't keep up.

154
00:10:46,684 --> 00:10:47,810
Do you know?

155
00:10:48,552 --> 00:10:51,953
There are two types of strong people,
genius types and effort types.

156
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:56,253
If your Sharingan is
a genius type drawing Uchiha ability...

157
00:10:56,894 --> 00:11:00,955
I'm an effort type who has
patiently mastered only Taijutsu.

158
00:11:02,666 --> 00:11:03,655
In a manner of speaking,

159
00:11:03,734 --> 00:11:08,262
your Sharingan and my ultimate
Taijutsu have the worst compatibility...

160
00:11:08,772 --> 00:11:09,761
<i>Guard!</i>

161
00:11:21,685 --> 00:11:23,277
Huh?! Dancing Leaf Shadow!

162
00:11:24,154 --> 00:11:26,213
And I shall prove it with this technique.

163
00:11:29,326 --> 00:11:31,851
Prove that effort exceeds the genius.

164
00:11:32,062 --> 00:11:34,030
<i>W-What's he going to do...?!</i>

165
00:11:35,499 --> 00:11:36,557
It's my victory!

166
00:11:45,076 --> 00:11:46,407
Huh?! Dancing Leaf Shadow!

167
00:11:47,111 --> 00:11:49,306
And I shall prove it with this technique.

168
00:11:51,682 --> 00:11:54,276
Prove that effort exceeds the genius.

169
00:11:55,019 --> 00:11:56,509
<i>W-What's he going to do...?!</i>

170
00:11:57,721 --> 00:11:58,915
It's my victory!

171
00:12:00,658 --> 00:12:01,317
Huh?!

172
00:12:04,361 --> 00:12:05,828
- Huh?
- Huh?!

173
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,088
That's...!

174
00:12:07,665 --> 00:12:09,792
That's as far as it goes! Lee!

175
00:12:15,406 --> 00:12:17,101
<i>W-What is it...?</i>
<i>What's going on?</i>

176
00:12:18,709 --> 00:12:19,767
Sasuke!

177
00:12:28,752 --> 00:12:30,344
<i>Sasuke was beaten?!</i>

178
00:12:30,588 --> 00:12:33,819
<i>What happened while</i>
<i>I was knocked out?!</i>

179
00:12:37,628 --> 00:12:39,493
Are you okay?! Sasuke.

180
00:12:41,365 --> 00:12:45,961
<i>He's agitated...</i>
<i>To think he couldn't fall properly.</i>

181
00:12:47,505 --> 00:12:49,166
Y-You were watching...?

182
00:12:50,341 --> 00:12:53,742
Lee! That technique just now
is prohibited, you know!

183
00:12:54,745 --> 00:12:57,441
<i>W-What's with that turtle...?</i>

184
00:12:58,082 --> 00:13:00,915
I-I'm sorry.
I didn't mean to...

185
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,551
<i>He's...getting scolded or something...</i>

186
00:13:05,923 --> 00:13:09,950
<i>Could that be...Bushy Brow's teacher?!</i>

187
00:13:15,833 --> 00:13:17,858
B-But, of course,

188
00:13:17,935 --> 00:13:23,032
I didn't even remotely have
a mind to use the Hidden technique...

189
00:13:23,207 --> 00:13:24,868
<i>There's no mistake!</i>

190
00:13:25,509 --> 00:13:26,305
- Huh?
- Huh?

191
00:13:26,710 --> 00:13:28,200
Hey-hey.

192
00:13:28,612 --> 00:13:29,601
What...?

193
00:13:30,481 --> 00:13:33,712
That thing... It's a turtle, right?
Right?

194
00:13:33,784 --> 00:13:35,615
Isn't it obvious?!

195
00:13:35,886 --> 00:13:39,617
Say! Say! Can even a turtle
become a Ninja teacher?

196
00:13:39,924 --> 00:13:41,551
I don't know!

197
00:13:41,759 --> 00:13:43,021
Fool!

198
00:13:44,028 --> 00:13:47,054
You think such subterfuge will work?!

199
00:13:47,531 --> 00:13:49,829
You should know very well what
it means

200
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:53,927
for a Shinobi to give away
his technique!

201
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:55,937
I... I know.

202
00:13:58,576 --> 00:14:02,012
<i>To think I lost to someone so flippant...</i>

203
00:14:06,517 --> 00:14:08,883
Have you prepared yourself?

204
00:14:09,119 --> 00:14:10,381
Y-Yes sir...

205
00:14:11,689 --> 00:14:14,852
All right, if you will, Guy Sensei!

206
00:14:18,295 --> 00:14:22,061
Man! Life treating you good, huh?

207
00:14:22,132 --> 00:14:23,099
Huh?!

208
00:14:25,102 --> 00:14:29,505
Whoaaa! An even more
intense guy has appeared!

209
00:14:29,573 --> 00:14:30,540
Yo, Lee!

210
00:14:32,576 --> 00:14:35,374
Super intense.
The extreme bowl cut...

211
00:14:35,713 --> 00:14:38,341
T-Those are some incredibly
raging brows...

212
00:14:38,415 --> 00:14:41,179
I've never seen anything like that
in my life.

213
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:46,988
H-Hey! You guys!
Don't mock Guy Sensei!

214
00:14:47,224 --> 00:14:49,021
Shut up!

215
00:14:49,326 --> 00:14:50,918
I'm at a loss for a reaction because

216
00:14:50,987 --> 00:14:52,648
of those bizarre things appearing
one after another!

217
00:14:52,730 --> 00:14:53,822
What?!

218
00:14:54,064 --> 00:14:55,429
Hey, Lee! Drop it!

219
00:14:57,868 --> 00:14:58,596
Yes, sir...

220
00:15:02,539 --> 00:15:04,006
Idiot!

221
00:15:16,453 --> 00:15:19,149
Lee, you... you...

222
00:15:19,456 --> 00:15:21,151
S-Sensei...!

223
00:15:23,093 --> 00:15:24,390
L-Lee...

224
00:15:25,696 --> 00:15:29,063
Sensei... I... I...

225
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:32,892
Enough, Lee!
Don't say anything!

226
00:15:34,171 --> 00:15:35,604
Sensei!

227
00:15:35,839 --> 00:15:36,828
Lee!

228
00:15:41,645 --> 00:15:43,909
<i>I lost to a guy like that...</i>

229
00:15:44,348 --> 00:15:47,044
Yes... <i>this</i> is adolescence!

230
00:15:47,117 --> 00:15:48,709
Sensei!

231
00:15:52,156 --> 00:15:55,091
That sort of tone's kind of nice, too.

232
00:15:55,459 --> 00:15:58,087
I-Idiot! That's dangerous!
Very dangerous!

233
00:15:59,963 --> 00:16:01,294
It's okay, Lee!

234
00:16:01,932 --> 00:16:05,060
Mistakes come with adolescence.
Don't worry about it!

235
00:16:05,469 --> 00:16:08,131
You're so kind... Sensei!

236
00:16:09,239 --> 00:16:14,006
Now then, take a hundred laps around
the Training Field toward that setting sun!

237
00:16:14,078 --> 00:16:15,705
Yes! Sensei!

238
00:16:28,525 --> 00:16:29,457
Let's go!

239
00:16:29,526 --> 00:16:30,390
Yes, sir!

240
00:16:31,729 --> 00:16:33,594
Hey, wait a minute.

241
00:16:33,697 --> 00:16:35,927
We're still in the middle
of the conversation!

242
00:16:36,100 --> 00:16:37,931
What're you going to do
about the Chunin Exam?!

243
00:16:38,202 --> 00:16:39,692
There's no time!

244
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:43,330
Huh? Oh, that's right...

245
00:16:45,175 --> 00:16:49,703
Lee, you will be punished for attempting
to break the prohibition on top of fighting...

246
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:53,580
in principle, after
the Chunin Exam.

247
00:16:53,684 --> 00:16:54,548
Okay!

248
00:16:54,885 --> 00:16:57,581
Five hundred howls of adolescence!

249
00:16:57,654 --> 00:16:58,518
Yes, sir!

250
00:17:02,326 --> 00:17:03,088
Idiots...

251
00:17:03,394 --> 00:17:04,725
Say! Say!

252
00:17:04,928 --> 00:17:07,226
By the way, what's with that turtle?

253
00:17:08,766 --> 00:17:10,825
<i>If I'm not mistaken, those kids are...</i>

254
00:17:10,901 --> 00:17:12,266
<i>Kakashi's...</i>

255
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:16,064
Oh! No, he's looking this way!

256
00:17:16,774 --> 00:17:19,834
You guys... how's Kakashi Sensei?

257
00:17:20,110 --> 00:17:21,668
You know Kakashi...?

258
00:17:22,179 --> 00:17:23,646
I know him all too well.

259
00:17:25,883 --> 00:17:31,082
People call us...
eternal rivals.

260
00:17:31,422 --> 00:17:33,219
Sounds like a lie!

261
00:17:33,290 --> 00:17:36,054
What're you saying?!
Guy Sensei really is...

262
00:17:36,126 --> 00:17:37,286
That's fine.

263
00:17:37,928 --> 00:17:40,522
"Action speaks louder than words"
anyway.

264
00:17:44,601 --> 00:17:45,431
Huh?!

265
00:17:48,238 --> 00:17:52,106
By the way, my record is fifty wins
and forty-nine losses.

266
00:17:52,176 --> 00:17:52,835
Huh?!

267
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:54,241
<i>This guy...</i>

268
00:17:55,245 --> 00:17:56,678
When did he.?

269
00:17:57,047 --> 00:18:01,279
One thing, I'm stronger than Kakashi...

270
00:18:02,619 --> 00:18:04,143
<i>N-No way...</i>

271
00:18:04,521 --> 00:18:09,220
<i>He's fast! He's faster than Kakashi!</i>
<i>Is he human...?!</i>

272
00:18:09,693 --> 00:18:12,924
How about that?!
Guy Sensei is awesome, isn't he?!

273
00:18:13,096 --> 00:18:14,358
<i>Darn it...</i>

274
00:18:14,565 --> 00:18:16,829
This time around,
Lee caused the trouble.

275
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:19,494
Out of consideration for my face,
forgive him.

276
00:18:19,837 --> 00:18:22,829
Out of consideration for
this pleasant face.

277
00:18:22,906 --> 00:18:25,238
<i>He's better than that Kakashi...?</i>

278
00:18:26,076 --> 00:18:28,840
<i>Darn it! He's...</i>

279
00:18:29,513 --> 00:18:31,208
<i>not just all talk...</i>

280
00:18:32,182 --> 00:18:36,414
You guys and Lee should probably go
to the classroom pretty soon.

281
00:18:44,561 --> 00:18:45,459
<i>He...!</i>

282
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:52,797
Then, do your best, Lee!
Farewell!

283
00:18:53,036 --> 00:18:53,832
Yes, sir.

284
00:18:54,004 --> 00:18:54,732
What?!

285
00:18:57,975 --> 00:18:58,873
Sasuke...

286
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:02,174
I have one last thing to tell you.

287
00:19:02,813 --> 00:19:07,841
I actually came here to
verify my own ability.

288
00:19:10,354 --> 00:19:12,151
I lied before.

289
00:19:13,190 --> 00:19:18,355
The strongest man of the
Leaf Village Genin might be on my team.

290
00:19:22,633 --> 00:19:25,966
I'm entering in order
to defeat that person.

291
00:19:26,737 --> 00:19:29,399
And, you are one of my targets.

292
00:19:31,308 --> 00:19:33,868
Please prepare yourself for the Exam!

293
00:19:43,954 --> 00:19:44,943
Sasuke...

294
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:48,381
Ha! So...

295
00:19:48,692 --> 00:19:51,923
I guess Uchiha clan's not all that, huh?

296
00:19:52,195 --> 00:19:53,321
Naruto!

297
00:19:54,765 --> 00:19:55,857
Shut up!

298
00:19:57,100 --> 00:19:59,227
I'll knock him flat next time!

299
00:19:59,403 --> 00:20:01,871
Ha! That from someone
who just got whipped.

300
00:20:01,939 --> 00:20:05,204
Hey... what's your problem?!
Naruto, you!

301
00:20:09,713 --> 00:20:12,910
You saw it, didn't you? His hand...

302
00:20:17,454 --> 00:20:20,855
That Bushy Brow probably did a heck
of a lot of special training.

303
00:20:21,058 --> 00:20:22,616
Day after day...

304
00:20:23,393 --> 00:20:24,951
More than you have...

305
00:20:27,965 --> 00:20:29,728
That's all it is.

306
00:20:35,872 --> 00:20:36,930
<i>Sasuke...</i>

307
00:20:48,151 --> 00:20:49,277
<i>Interesting...</i>

308
00:20:50,988 --> 00:20:51,818
Hmph!

309
00:20:52,823 --> 00:20:57,453
It's starting to get interesting...
the Chunin Exam!

310
00:20:57,527 --> 00:20:59,051
What's next?

311
00:21:01,932 --> 00:21:02,864
Yeah!

312
00:21:02,933 --> 00:21:03,490
All right!

313
00:21:05,602 --> 00:21:09,060
Let's go, Naruto! Sakura!

314
00:21:09,406 --> 00:21:10,373
Yeah!

315
00:22:52,209 --> 00:22:55,201
Whoaaaa!
There are tons of people here!

316
00:22:55,446 --> 00:22:57,778
Are they all here to take
the Chunin Exam?

317
00:22:57,915 --> 00:23:01,180
Ino, Shikamaru, Choji, Kiba,
Shino, Hinata and Rock Lee?

318
00:23:01,251 --> 00:23:02,775
So you're all here, too?

319
00:23:02,853 --> 00:23:05,447
Yeah, I'm pumped, pumped, pumped!

320
00:23:05,522 --> 00:23:09,458
Open up your eyes and watch me
become the Hokage!

321
00:23:10,127 --> 00:23:13,619
Next episode:
"Genin Takedown!
All Nine Rookies Face Off!"

322
00:23:13,730 --> 00:23:16,563
As for me,
I'm going to kick butt once again!
